{"tid":2435217,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"軍情動態》 日美法部隊首次日本國內聯演 日方規劃最快5月後舉辦","createTime":"2021-03-06T05:39:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T16:03:21.000Z","uid":141151,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4dae777ecc43cf835c7778b654eb11ddcde6ecb9","tid":2435217,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T05:39:05.000Z","msg":"軍情動態》 日美法部隊首次日本國內聯演 日方規劃最快5月後舉辦<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3457398\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3457398&d=vOSJ0XARgdQWnSR9BVy1n%2F56hpy2SSQtx6ElJ%2BvIbMI%3D&h=0e602c67\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3457398&h=77c40764\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3457398</a><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕制約中國在即！日本陸上自衛隊陸上幕僚長湯淺悟郎昨天（4日）在記者會上透露，正協調與法軍、美軍在日本國內進行聯演，並稱擁有共同價值觀的國家進行合作，將有助於印太區域穩定。他還表示，目前規模與聯演參與人員尚未有定論，最快得等到5月以後，而這也是三國陸上部隊首次齊聚日本聯演。<br />\n<br />\n據日本《共同社》5日報導，湯淺悟郎昨天（4日）在記者會上指出，目前正協調在日本國內與法國陸軍、美國海軍陸戰隊舉辦聯演事宜，<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">如協調成功，這將是首次日本、美國、法國三國陸上部隊在日本進行正式訓練，而日本防衛省與自衛隊義在維持「自由開放的印度太平洋」條件下，擴大與美國及歐洲的合作關係，以「制約中國」。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n《共同社》指出，針對聯演規模與地點等，湯淺悟郎稱目前尚未做出決定，並提及「最快也要到5月以後」。湯淺悟郎強調，「擁有共同價值觀的國家深化合作的信號將有助於印度太平洋的穩定。聯合訓練極有意義」，而歐陸各國亦出於對中國加強海洋活動的警惕，陸續派出部隊前往太平洋地區。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，除了陸自消息外，《共同社》 3日報導，日本海上自衛隊當天於官網宣佈，上月26日在美屬關島周邊海域，日方「夕霧號」護衛艦與西班牙海軍船艦「胡安&middot;塞巴斯提安&middot;艾爾卡諾」（Juan Sebasti&aacute;n de Elcano）進行聯演，旨在增進日本與西班牙海軍的相互了解和信任，而報導亦提及，日本海自「意在擴大加強合作的範圍從而牽制中國」。"},{"pid":"a54af1fbc04a57ea7c6881d56a25270afd20c819","tid":2435217,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T06:09:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6119cac41077849c0a03cb741bf5339e1693c75e","tid":2435217,"uid":60470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T06:12:47.000Z","msg":"法國都黎埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"543321441747fb5e1cd02521f7921b6e96de19ac","tid":2435217,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T02:24:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"935646fcb769ff971e906bdd79507500c7602b7d","tid":2435217,"uid":337119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T15:02:25.000Z","msg":"打爆CCP<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98b9ce452c91164ec125ea65a990e0735546d68a","tid":2435217,"uid":218158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T15:59:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"779dcf9ae42812aee36bc2212e69c0ea1d9abab7","tid":2435217,"uid":92448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T16:03:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}